In [7]:
#%matplotlib inline

from scipy.ndimage.filters import median_filter as mf

for loop in range(1, 5):
    i_m = mf(img, size = loop)   
    plt.figure(figsize=(4, 4))  
    plt.imshow(i_m, cmap="gray")
    plt.title(loop)
plt.show()
In [9]:
#%matplotlib inline
#pip install tqdm
from tqdm import *

from scipy.ndimage.filters import median_filter as mf

for loop in tqdm(range(1, 15)):
    i_m = mf(img, size = loop)   
    #print('size {}'.format(loop))
    plt.figure(figsize=(4, 4))  
    plt.imshow(i_m,  cmap="gray")
    plt.title(loop)
plt.show()
